Uses of Package
dtconsole

  • Classes in dtconsole used by dtconsole 
    Class and Description
    DengueFighter
    DengueFighter class act as a controller for the Dengue Fighter Stimulator maintain a collection of site and collection of resources
    Grade
    Grade is an enumerated type (enum) that takes on values V_LOW (Very Low), LOW, MEDIUM, HIGH and V_HIGH (Very High).Each of the grades has a multiplier from 1 to 5 respectively.
    Resource
    Resource class is a abstract class that should be allocated to each site
    ResourceUsage
    ResourceUsage class save the assign resources
    Site
    The Site represents a potential dengue site to be used in the DengueFighter game.The sites are created with randomly generated values for the attributes.A constant is used for the infection rate.Current infection rate used is 0.15 - 0.27 in Selangor (Ridpest)
